# MT25009
# Graduate Systems (CSE638) – PA02
# Network I/O Primitives Analysis using perf

==================================================
OVERVIEW
==================================================

This assignment experimentally studies the cost of
data movement in network I/O by implementing:

A1 – Two-copy socket communication (send/recv)
A2 – One-copy optimized communication (sendmsg + iovec)
A3 – Zero-copy communication (MSG_ZEROCOPY)

Each version is implemented as a multithreaded
TCP client–server program and profiled using perf.


==================================================
