MT25009_Part_E_Report.pdf


==================================================
COMPILATION
==================================================

make

This generates:

A1S A1C
A2S A2C
A3S A3C


==================================================
RUNNING PROGRAMS
==================================================

Open TWO terminals.

Terminal 1 (Server):
--------------------
./A1S
(or ./A2S or ./A3S)

Terminal 2 (Client):
--------------------
./A1C <threads> <size> <duration>

Example:
./A1C 4 4096 5


==================================================
PERF PROFILING
==================================================

Example:

perf stat -e cycles,cache-misses,L1-dcache-load-misses,context-switches \
./A1C 4 4096 5


==================================================
AUTOMATED EXPERIMENTS
==================================================

chmod +x run_bench.sh
./run_bench.sh

Outputs:
results.csv


==================================================
PLOTTING
==================================================

(As required, values are hardcoded in python file)

python3 MT25009_Part_D_Plots.py

This generates plots during demo.


